core.name: Kingdom And State Aboat Time Blue Print Bikini Bottom
core.description: You’ve kept it long enough girl. You’ve made some wonderful memories together—you and your swimsuit … your –old- swimsuit from a decade ago. But it’s Aboat Time to let go and get a new one. A nice shiny yacht awaits, with a nice, hopefully decent guy on it, and you want to show up looking your best. And you can’t wear that old thing. If you really, really, really must hold on to some part of it, then cut that bad boy up and use the fabric somehow by making something using a DIY you find on Pinterest. But for the love of all things fashionable, buy this new suit. Your gym bill will thank you. And so will your date (assuming he’s a gentleman, of course). core.name: Look Your Cutest Gray Plaid Dress
core.description: Ah yes, like ye olde tale of mischief, trespass, and thievery, there’s a Goldilocks rule to fashion. When stealing the hearts of unwary bears (and by bears, we mean handsome, would-be suitors), you want to be just the right amount of cute. Too cute, and you’re decked out in Sanrio’s, complete with fuzzy pink hair clips, multi-colored nail polish, and an adorable Hello Kitty pencil case/clutch. Not cute enough, and you’re likely to be mistaken for “just one of the guys.” No, you want to be just cute enough, in a dashing plaid dress for instance, so you can look your cutest, without breaking the paramount Goldilocks rule. Model is wearing a small. • 100% Cotton 100% Rayon Lining • Hand Wash Cold • Lined • Imported

core.name: Lost With You Pants
core.description: I know it’s hard-wired into your DNA not to stop and ask for directions, but if you’re aware of the problem, shouldn’t you be trying some self-improvement or something? I mean, it’s almost dark out, we haven’t passed a gas station for 20 miles, and it’s starting to look like we may be sleeping in the back of the car. Lucky for you, I know how to enjoy the experience. Because being Lost With You is still better than knowing exactly where I am but not having you to nuzzle up to … even if you’re too thick-headed to avoid getting lost in the first place. Now pull over, I have to tinkle. Pants feature elastic waistband and ankle cuffs, drawstring tie, functional front pockets, pleat detailing. Unlined. 50% Polyester, 50% Polyurethane. Wash by hand in cold water. core.name: Remain Palm Pink Print Shorts
core.description: We have some bad news, but we need you to Remain Palm. You see, our three-hour tour might end up running a little over after that storm we ran into, and now we’re stranded on this deserted island. We know it’ll be a bit onerous having to spend your days in a tropical paradise, drinking pineapple juice out of the hollowed husks of coconuts, but the three dozen strapping massage therapists that were on board the SS Minnow have volunteered their services to help ease your suffering while we wait to be rescued (although, admittedly, we’re not holding out much hope for our efforts to fashion a short wave radio out of sea shells and palm fronds). So do try to relax—slip into a cute pair of shorts, and enjoy your beachside massage. And please accept our most heartfelt apologies for any inconvenience this may have caused.
